Key Match Events: Cameroon defeated Namibia with a scoreline of 1-0 in the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations qualifying match.
Aboubakar scored the winning goal for Cameroon in the 65th minute.
Pre-Game Insights: Cameroon and Namibia were drawn in Group C for the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations qualifying campaign.
Cameroon had a strong recent form with two wins and two draws in their World Cup qualifiers.
Namibia had a decent run in the COSAFA Cup and World Cup qualifiers before the match.
The match was expected to be a competitive encounter between two sides with contrasting forms.
